DESCRIPTION
========================
Sakura no Ki no Shita is the second studio album by 
Japanese singer Aiko, released on March 1, 2000. It reached 
#1 in the Japanese charts, and had several hit singles. 
The music on it is a fusion of jazz, rock and j-pop.

Read more @ https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sakura_no_Ki_no_Shita
